	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Decent<span id=notbold>[3.00]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>Sharing my encounter to hopefully help others.<br><br>Completed all quest steps (except final mob) in a couple hours.<br><br>Saturday, Jan 04 2003 - 11am PST - 9pm PST camped for rare vampyre (final spawn)&nbsp;&nbsp;He spawned at 9pm PST.  Killed lvl 58 mob, wiped on 62, got back called in re enforcements.  Mob despawned in 30 minutes from lack of engagement.<br><br>Sunday Jan 05 2003 - 11am PST - 3pm PST camped for rare vampyre (final spawn)  He spawned at 3:00pm EST.  Kited the lvl 58 mob until people were enroute.  He despawned during kiting and 62 mob spawned.  Kited him, kited, kited... add vamp, add vamp, add vamp.  Trained vamps outside, re enforcements took out all vamps.  Named wouldnt come down stairs, through excellect efforts of Palarran, my loveable druid friend, we got it outside, where him and another druid kited.<br><br>Mob died at 5pm PST.<br><br>Stragity of slaughter,<br><br>Aggro kite with pets wearing bane weaps<br>Nukers nuke<br>Melee's taunt only if kiter loses aggro.<br><br><br>Seru graphic on the shield (2 headed eagle) but i wear it on my back :)<br><br>&nbsp;<br>Zarkarin Laiquasse<br>65th Archon of Ayonae Ro</td></tr>
